You teach golf, for example.

69
00:02:47,380 --> 00:02:49,040
We can't really
include something

70
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:50,750
in a performance
standard that's really

71
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:54,440
outside of the control of
that individual employee.

72
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:56,820
And it can also need to
be based on observations.

73
00:02:56,820 --> 00:02:59,100
So we need to observe what
