So we've already put some
performance standards together.

83
00:03:19,540 --> 00:03:22,450
And often the next
step may be observing

84
00:03:22,450 --> 00:03:23,839
the employee's behavior.

85
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:26,930
So observing some of
the tasks or activities

86
00:03:26,930 --> 00:03:29,590
that they may do,
that you can observe,

87
00:03:29,590 --> 00:03:31,570
that will show you or
give you some indication

