is to always allow
adequate time.

135
00:05:30,430 --> 00:05:32,787
If it's rushed, too
short, too long,

136
00:05:32,787 --> 00:05:34,620
you won't get the
information that you want.

137
00:05:34,620 --> 00:05:36,960
Or you often get people
tired at the end of it,

138
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:39,330
and not really giving
accurate information.

139
00:05:39,330 --> 00:05:41,510
You need to be
prepared in that you've

