00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:52,420
So it needs to be
planned out ahead.

145
00:05:52,420 --> 00:05:54,240
And in terms of
being prepared, you

146
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:57,730
need to have had a look
at their self-appraisal,

147
00:05:57,730 --> 00:05:59,920
and then thought
OK, why have they

